{"tid":2462844,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"杜汶澤譏新疆棉下跪藝人只追求錢和名氣︰地面一切離他們很遠","createTime":"2021-03-26T09:04:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T09:12:06.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fbcf4d248fde1a6188fd95fb7e9da11e8bb7a3ac","tid":2462844,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/m0Y3i5iE6T_0pUrZonQobsMWhhk=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FZ7KP5ZW3RCSNK3RKCAKJBGSLU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fm0Y3i5iE6T_0pUrZonQobsMWhhk%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFZ7KP5ZW3RCSNK3RKCAKJBGSLU.jpg&h=82b4b3de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n杜汶澤目前仍然身在台灣，為自家網台「喱騷」拍攝節目，不過他依然留意香港新聞，日前先挑機「楊明無罪」，再嘲「林鍾大戰」，非常好火。對於外國品牌終止購買新疆棉花事件，昨日一班藝人陳奕迅（Eason）、彭于晏、陳偉霆（的士陳）、楊穎（Angelababy）為向大陸表忠，火速同代言品牌割席，阿澤昨日在Facebook已食住花生連開數帖，到今日他再為藝人「發聲」，指普羅fans對偶像有期待，只是一廂情願的想法。<br />\n<br />\n自從Eason等藝人相繼跪低後，fans們都在社交平台留言，大部份都是針對Eason，反問他「咁好笑嘅，為棉花發聲，但人權問題就唔出聲」，更引用他首歌《陀飛輪》歌詞「靈魂若變賣了，上鏈也沒心跳」。不過阿澤今日在FB以「藝人舔共」為題，發長文「撥亂反正」，一開頭就講到觀眾對藝人們下跪，感到而失望甚至憤怒時，會問「已經那麼有錢，還這樣！有必要嗎？」「難道生命受威脅？」「為什麼他們會變成這樣？」，其實這些完全出於普羅大眾的誤解。他還說藝人成名得來不易，自然相當珍惜，而絕大部份藝人，特別是層次較高的藝人，事實上對社會並不關心，他們眼中「除了錢、名氣和工作上的滿足感之外，地面上所發生的一切，離他們很遠。」<br />\n<br />\n阿澤呼籲fans不要對偶像太認真，因為「感到失望，只因你沒有做好期望管理而已。」以後有歌就聽、有戲就看，不要有幻想。阿澤自言對對佔中、反送中運動表態導致被封殺，是因為從小就脾氣差，亦「只怪我天生睪丸酮數太高」所致。發文不到4小時已有3萬多人給「like」，超過1,700多人分享。不少留言相當抵死，特別是林子博話：「睪丸酮太高？咁我明喇！原來因為你有兩粒，咁一粒可能會好啲！」嘲諷Eason當年演唱會跌落台，下體受傷撞爆睪丸。另外，吳日言昨日為喱騷開工，她在IG感謝阿澤關照，又話「為咗個飯碗，有啲人可以去到好盡」，但她相信世界餓不死人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/A8MT-ZzJkm99qExYshfPAOZQuSg=/802x1005/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IFG5GGEVH5CPVETZ5FS4M5T7GY.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FA8MT-ZzJkm99qExYshfPAOZQuSg%3D%2F802x1005%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIFG5GGEVH5CPVETZ5FS4M5T7GY.JPG&h=f453938c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/aKlCefwB_Kk0R0pyu3TYMxJO4tE=/802x644/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KZ26VCZZMJCSVCHVHFJLN5DGRE.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FaKlCefwB_Kk0R0pyu3TYMxJO4tE%3D%2F802x644%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKZ26VCZZMJCSVCHVHFJLN5DGRE.JPG&h=1ca79b5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/42h7VCyn474ciQjmz58qIhF0xwg=/802x601/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LUXE3R3GPBAMLHTFWHIL2XXWPA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F42h7VCyn474ciQjmz58qIhF0xwg%3D%2F802x601%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLUXE3R3GPBAMLHTFWHIL2XXWPA.jpg&h=b0882587&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Zx3LwdAmvAbIEvmGteWR4AwhXvk=/802x641/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SLFSI6VBTFHPTNPT2XINJ4WIQQ.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZx3LwdAmvAbIEvmGteWR4AwhXvk%3D%2F802x641%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSLFSI6VBTFHPTNPT2XINJ4WIQQ.JPG&h=97cd93e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3Cu181e--U9Xlz4OjsHlCNWefMo=/802x587/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CFNE35SEARE77C7BGSHFOR5OPM.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3Cu181e--U9Xlz4OjsHlCNWefMo%3D%2F802x587%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCFNE35SEARE77C7BGSHFOR5OPM.JPG&h=be82cda7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210326/XSFZCHF7TZFEHELHYXPDSTMXLY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210326%2FXSFZCHF7TZFEHELHYXPDSTMXLY%2F&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1Gh0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=e1b19e36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210326%2FXSFZCHF7TZFEHELHYXPDSTMXLY%2F&h=f37ceb72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210326/XSFZCHF7TZFEHELHYXPDSTMXLY/</a>"},{"pid":"aa8b865591d2e4cc82d5e622e300cefc1a06ab98","tid":2462844,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:05:32.000Z","msg":"想要..<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b892190929c41f84460befa1322834472cc76661","tid":2462844,"uid":99908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:12:06.000Z","msg":"想睇黃金蝦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}